entries.title: British woman dies in avalanche in French Alps
entries.description: A British woman has died after getting caught in an avalanche in the French Alps.

entries.title: Hospital overcrowding in Ireland has become 'undoubtedly dangerous', emergency doctor warns
entries.description: A leading emergency medicine doctor has described Ireland's overcrowded hospitals as life-threatening - as the head of the health service admitted it was "realistic" that people had died as a result of the crisis.

entries.title: Plane carrying 72 people crashes in Nepal
entries.description: A plane carrying 72 people has crashed in Nepal,  officials have said.

entries.title: Tens of thousands of Israelis protest against Netanyahu's legal reforms
entries.description: Tens of thousands of protesters have taken to the streets in three Israeli cities to oppose plans by Benjamin Netanyahu's government to overhaul the country's legal system and weaken the Supreme Court.
